{"tid":2136811,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"DQ隨想- 陳惜姿","createTime":"2020-08-02T12:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T12:02:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"05d17faddde33163d035bb6c6532c5065c9b5220","tid":2136811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200725/DWETHKKQ5ZF43OUJ4CG3NVWRI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200725%2FDWETHKKQ5ZF43OUJ4CG3NVWRI4%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=5464b11c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200725%2FDWETHKKQ5ZF43OUJ4CG3NVWRI4%2F&h=782ca3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200725/DWETHKKQ5ZF43OUJ4CG3NVWRI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nDQ隨想- 陳惜姿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tJe_n20LX-e7UIQKO1sZzPz_01k=/4516x3011/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PATH7JAKDREJ7FZVMEYTVQOJBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtJe_n20LX-e7UIQKO1sZzPz_01k%3D%2F4516x3011%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPATH7JAKDREJ7FZVMEYTVQOJBE.jpg&h=fba165ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在立法會當反對派，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所以任何人肯承擔此責，我都由衷感激，議員放棄大好事業，把花樣年華消耗在虛無程序，投身醬缸中，為選民爭一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n港府要止暴制亂，把民意轉移到議會本是最好方法。議會制度之原意，是把反對聲音吸納，意見在議會反映了，便不用相見於怒火街頭。去年暴烈示威過後，抗爭派肯走入議會，執政者本應歡呼叫好。他們的選民正是街頭抗爭者，抗爭派進入議會，原是解決問題的開始。<br />\n<br />\n可惜為官者沒此智慧，卻反其道而行。這次大型DQ，影響整個非建制派光譜，把抗爭派、溫和派的選民一併得罪了，那可是超過一半的香港人口，香港以後如何管治，中央有沒有想過後果？<br />\n<br />\n若DQ後還要延遲選舉，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我們是烽火下危城裏悲微的倖存者，。。。。。。。。。。"}]}